question: Show $150 wellness programs and day spas.
sql_query1:
SELECT Day_Spa.name
FROM Day_Spa
WHERE Day_Spa.Price = 150
UNION
SELECT Wellness_Retreat.name
FROM Wellness_Retreat
WHERE Wellness_Retreat.Price = 150
sql_query2:

interpretation1: Show me $150 wellness programs and $150 day spas.
interpretation2: Show all day spas and $150 wellness programs.
